{"tid":1623872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：未來三日是長假期，和理非的遊行示威已經沒有可能","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T02:39:20.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8265eedbd21680c632d3506981b75600ab183459","tid":1623872,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4a45Cy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4a45Cy.jpg&h=0d2c0ab5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2768feca0325fb23f0ab51d2938a7ac81b57922","tid":1623872,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"未來三日是長假期，「勇武」主導的黑衣暴力會持續升級，「和理非」的遊行示威已經沒有可能。<br />\n<br />\n暴徒的行動會越來越激烈，接近或等同恐襲級別，暴徒的成份也會越來越複雜。大範圍的鐵路、其他公共交通設施，公共場所、商鋪和食肆會無差別地被打、砸、燒。請大家尤其是青少年和婦女盡量減少外出，避免妨礙警察執法。各新聞機構應慎重考慮是否適宜繼續派遣記者上火線。<br />\n<br />\n同時，黑暴亦會將心戰升級，網上的謡言和恫嚇會增加，包括航機撞樓、超市搶購、銀行擠提、汽油短缺等，目的是動搖信心，製造恐慌，破壞穩定，這些都是慣用技倆，大家要沉著應對，要用常識常理分辨真偽，不要將虛假失實或誇大的消息轉發。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100010574583275/posts/949513532077791?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100010574583275%2Fposts%2F949513532077791%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=9dbec6fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100010574583275/posts/949513532077791?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"41a8a632b7664d2c3ce26c300bc6f7f207a166c7","tid":1623872,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cf2c96a05ff23b1d1cde84516cbcf53fa2ddd7","tid":1623872,"uid":144492,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:09:41.000Z","msg":"屌你個閪呀<br />\n唔批民陣嘅遊行跟手講呢啲<br />\n真係公就你贏字就我輸喎"},{"pid":"1275ba0d8885ea8fb14e2